async Task SaveAsync()  
{  
 await myStream.WriteAllBytesAsync();  
 await myStream.FlushAsync();  
}

how to do correct ?

async Task SaveAsync()  
{  
var task1 = myStream.WriteAllBytesAsync();  
var task2 = myStream.FlushAsync();  
await task1; await task2;   
}  
maybe ?  
but what about the exceptions?

Thanks !
